statements.sql: select count(id) as total from  (SELECT @row_no:=@row_no+1 as row_no, a.id ,a.name ,a.hardconfig,CONCAT('[',a.brand_id ,']',b.name) as brand_name,CONCAT('[',a.class_id,']',c.name) as class_name FROM device_model a ,(select  @row_no:=0) t  ,device_brand b,device_class c where a.brand_id=b.id and a.class_id=c.id  and c.id in(6,7,8,9,11,13,14,12,16,21,22,17,2,3,4,18,15,19,5,20,23) ) z
